### Get latest cars
GET http://localhost:5500/api/cars

###

### Filter by make
GET http://localhost:5500/api/cars?make=Toyota

###

### Filter by model
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cars?model=Harrier

###

### Filter by year
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cars?year=2022

###

### Filter by price range
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cars?minPrice=20000000&maxPrice=50000000

###

### Get single vehicle
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cars/1

###

### Create vehicle
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cars
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "vin":"123ABC",
  "make":"Toyota",
  "model":"Harrier",
  "year":2022,
  "price":45000000,
  "mileage":5000
}